Author: PistachioTeddyBear
Text: Oh totally I relate! I'm 27f, had EDNOS/OSFED since around...15 or 16. Before it was binge, restrict, restrict EXERCISE with a handful of orthorexic behaviours thrown in and counting my calories like they were money. Now I'm just BINGE BINGE BINGE caffeine and adderall, watching portion sizes, aaand I'm probably going to drop hella weight by the summertime again.
